lick NEXT and you\'ll see the final step, which is to verify your contact information. If anything needs to be fixed click \"PREVIOUS\" and correct the errors. If everything looks correct click \"REGISTER ME\" to complete your registration.</li>\r\n<li>That\'s it. Your registration is complete and your team has been created. You\'ll receive a confirmation email with a link to your personal page.</li>\r\n<li>You\'ll be presented with an opportunity to start fundraising right away by emailing people you know and asking for donations. You can also connect with Facebook by scrolling down to the GET SOCIAL section and clicking \"GET STARTED\". If you\'d like to skip the items on this page for now you can click \"SKIP THIS STEP\" and you\'ll be brought to your Participant Center, where you can click \"TEAM\" to manage and recruit for your team; \"FUNDRAISING\" to start asking for donations; or \"PROFILE\" to edit your personal profile. Keep an eye out for Participant Center help documentation and videos on your event\'s website</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"border:1px solid gray; padding-left:20px;\">\r\n	<p><strong>If you need help...</strong></p>\r\n\r\n	<p>Please contact us if you need assistance. We\'re here to help!</p>\r\n\r\n	<p><a href=\"mailto:donations@braintumor.org\">donations@braintumor.org</a><br />\r\n	866-455-3214</p>\r\n</div>','Participant Support: How to create a team during registration','','inherit','open','open','','2522-revision-v1','','','2014-07-04 16:03:32','2014-07-04 16:03:32','',2522,'http://events.braintumor.org/2522-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (2601,7,'2014-07-04 16:05:18','2014-07-04 16:05:18','Welcome to the <strong>Nashville Brain Tumor Race</strong>, an event to raise awareness and much-needed resources to fund critical brain tumor-specific programs to improve the lives of all those affected by brain tumors. Hosted by the National Brain Tumor Society, the Nashville Brain Tumor Race offers individuals and teams a chance to honor and remember loved ones, connect with others interested in the brain tumor cause, and helps to educate the local community on the diverse needs of the brain tumor community.\r\n\r\n<a title=\"View the full event details here\" href=\"http://events.braintumor.org/events/nashville-brain-tumor-race/event-details/\">View the full event details here</a>\r\n\r\nAll funds raised through our events allow the National Brain Tumor Society to advance research and public policy to improve the availability of new and better treatments, and fuel the discovery of a cure for brain tumors.\r\n\r\n<div id=\"help\" style=\"border:1px solid gray; padding:20px; margin-top:10px; margin-bottom:10px;\">\r\n	<strong>Need help getting started? <a href=\"http://events.braintumor.org/a-participant-support/\" title=\"Participant Support\" target=\"_blank\">View our instructions and video tutorials</a>.</strong>\r\n</div>','Nashville Brain Tumor Race','','inherit','open','open','','2200-revision-v1','','','2014-07-04 16:05:18','2014-07-04 16:05:18','',2200,'http://events.braintumor.org/2200-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0);
